        <updateDate>2005-11-09T19:35:19Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Reverse Mortgages to Help America's Seniors Act - Amends the National Housing Act to remove the aggregate and insurance benefit limitations on the number of home equity conversion (reverse) mortgages for elderly homeowners that may be insured by the Federal Housing Administration (FHA). </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
